        "## 5. 요약 비교\n",
        "\n",
        "| 문제 | $g(x)$ | $g'(x)$ 부호 | 수렴 패턴 | 근 |\n",
        "|------|--------|-------------|----------|----|\n",
        "| $x^2 - 5x - 7 = 0$ | $\\sqrt{5x+7}$ | $+$ | Staircase | $6.14 < x < 6.15$ |\n",
        "| $2 - x = \\tan x$ | $\\arctan(2-x)$ | $-$ | Cobweb | $0.85 < x < 0.86$ |\n",
        "| $xe^x = 2$ | $2e^{-x}$ | $-$ | Cobweb | $0.852 < x < 0.853$ |\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Cobweb vs Staircase**: $g'(x) > 0$ → Staircase, $g'(x) < 0$ → Cobweb"
